<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') %>

<div class="container mb-5 mt-3">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Prohibited Content Guidelines</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">
        At Boomerang, we're committed to fostering a creative and safe
        environment for our community. To maintain this standard, we prohibit
        projects and rewards that involve illegal activities, are heavily
        regulated, potentially harmful to backers, or violate our community
        principles.
    </p>
    <hr class="my-5" />

    <h2 class="mb-4">Prohibited Projects and Content</h2>
    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Medical Claims:</strong> Items or projects claiming to
            diagnose, cure, treat, or prevent an illness or condition.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Contests and Gambling:</strong> Contests, raffles, gambling,
            lotteries, or coupon-based projects.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Energy Consumables:</strong> Offering energy foods and
            drinks as rewards.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Offensive Material:</strong> Hate speech, content
            encouraging violence, or promoting intolerance.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Genetically Modified Organisms:</strong> Offering GMOs as
            rewards.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Live Animals:</strong> Including live animals as rewards.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Alcohol:</strong> Offering alcohol as a reward is
            prohibited.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Financial Services:</strong> Offering financial or
            money-processing services or instruments.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Political Fundraising:</strong> Fundraising for political
            campaigns or initiatives.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Explicit Content:</strong> Pornographic or explicit adult
            content.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Discriminatory Content:</strong> Promoting discrimination,
            bigotry, or intolerance.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Unoriginal Projects:</strong> Projects sharing or
            repackaging existing products without new value.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Resale of Items:</strong> Rewards must be produced or
            designed by the project creator—reselling is prohibited.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Drugs and Paraphernalia:</strong> Projects involving drugs,
            nicotine, tobacco, or related items.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Weapons:</strong> Weapons, replicas, and weapon accessories
            are prohibited.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <hr class="my-5" />

    <h2 class="mb-4">Need Clarification?</h2>
    <p class="text-center">
        If your project involves something illegal, heavily regulated, or
        potentially dangerous that isn’t listed here, please
        <a href="#" class="text-primary">contact us</a> before starting your
        project.
    </p>

    <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <a href="/projects/new" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
            >Start Your Project</a
        >
    </div>
</div>
